# Postview - Just write your posts ...

[Postview][] is a simple [_blogware_][blogware] written in [Ruby][] using [Sinatra][] [DSL][]
that renders files written in [Markdown][].

* Easy to configure.
* Easy to synchronize.

Fork the project and try.

